Normal-mode Part 1
====================
		
1.  j = move down (line)
		
2.  k = move up (line)

3.  h = move left (character)

4.  l = move right (character)

5.  ^ = move to beginning of line

6.  $ = move to end of line

7.  w = move to next word

8.  2w = move two words forward

9.  b = move to previous word

10. e = move to end word

11. x = delete 

12. X = delete backwards (backspace)

13. w = save

14. q = quit

15. q! = force quit (when it's all hosed)
